N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4111.3 - Misrepresentation in declaration

State Regulations
A misrepresentation, error or omission made in a
declaration may void the declaration and the person or persons responsible
therefor shall be subject to the penalties prescribed by this

Subchapter. Notes
